"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-26-novak-djokovic-responds-trolls-whod-love-retire-olympics-21305298\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Novak Djokovichas fired a message to the trolls who'd 'love' him to enter retirement after the Olympic tennis tournament atParis2024.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old GOAT is the figurehead of theBig Three eraof men's tennis, havingpassed Roger Federer and Rafael Nadal's tallyof major singles titles.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"score\": 0.7168567345960191, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GOAT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GOAT_(platform)\"}, {\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}, {\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Federerhas retired, while Nadal has struggled with injuries in recent years, with the 38-year-old's Olympic singles participationin doubt over a thigh issue.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.758245990383886e-16, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic, though, is still very much near the top of the sport - and came close to landing this year's Wimbledon title - only losing out toCarlos Alcarazin the final.\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serbian won three of the four Grand Slam tournaments in 2023 and despite a dip in form this season, he is adamant he hasno plans to hang up his racketat all.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.7214164799073621, \"rank\": 0.34569599764304176, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.9605092062913813, \"rank\": 0.04111443539514609, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not have retirement close in my mind, to be honest,' Djokovic said ahead of his Olympic singles first-round match against Australia's\\u00a0Matthew Ebden, and a potentialblockbuster second-round matchagainst Nadal, if the Spaniard is fit.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8360272971896196e-14, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999306517777264, \"rank\": 6.516893355730448e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Ebden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.758245990383886e-16, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9776423337479124, \"rank\": 0.022359719571527395, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even though I know a lot of people would love me to retire so this era is done.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think as long as there is at least one of us left competing, the era is still going.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Of course there is a change of generations.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have Alcaraz and [Jannik] Sinner, currently they are our two best players in the world, deservedly.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4622037094784795e-16, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They are playing at a very high level particularly this year.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are very young and they are going to carry this sport in the future.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I have been present for the shift of many generations in the last 15 years and I like to see that.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Novak Djokovic also sent a classy message to British legend Andy Murray ahead of his retirement from professional tennis.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9093884419395858, \"rank\": 0.09353433930680856, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.163356933825082e-61, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I heard the news about Andy,' Djokovic said.\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8360272971896196e-14, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope that he will have the best possible farewell in his last competitive match here in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a legend of our sport.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's been an incredibly important player for tennis globally.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Nadal of course, the same.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even more.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the results and achievements he's had particularly in this city, at Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal still did not say when his last tournament will be so hopefully for the sake of the sport he can keep going.'\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think it's also great that I am still able to play, Nadal, other veterans like [Stan] Wawrinka that have won multiple Grand Slams and made a big name in the sport.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think that also adds more significance and attention to our sport and I think it's a nice fine balance.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Of course, the end is closer than the beginning, I know that, for me personally as well.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I still enjoy competition and I will keep going until I do not enjoy it anymore.'\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:What are Olympic medals made from?\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 26